-402[5] "Product Information. Mevacor (lovastatin)." Merck & Co, Inc, West Point, PA.[6] Bailey DG, Malcolm J, Arnold O, Spence JD "Grapefruit juice-drug interactions." Br J Clin Pharmacol 46 (1998): 101-10[7] Neuvonen PJ, Backman JT, Niemi M "Pharmacokinetic comparison of the potential over-the-counter statins simvastatin, lovastatin, fluvastatin and pravastatin." Clin Pharmacokinet 47 (2008): 463-74[8] Thompson PD, Clarkson P, Karas RH "Statin-associated myopathy." JAMA 289 (2003): 1681-90[9] "Product Information. Zocor (simvastatin)." Merck & Co, Inc, West Point, PA.[10] "Product Information. Trikafta (elexacaftor/ivacaftor/tezacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[11] "Product Information. Kalydeco (ivacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[12] "Product Information. Orkambi (ivacaftor-lumacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[13] "Product Information. Symdeko 4-Week (ivacaftor-tezacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.', 1767369485);
